        <activityName xml:lang="en">fibre, flax, short, scutched to generic market for silky fibres</activityName>
        <includedActivitiesStart xml:lang="en">Activity starts with the reception of 'fibre, flax, short, scutched'.</includedActivitiesStart>
        <includedActivitiesEnd xml:lang="en">Activity ends with the 'silky fibres'.</includedActivitiesEnd>
        <generalComment>
          <text xml:lang="en" index="0">This is a renaming activity. It's purpose is to link 'fibre, flax, short, scutched' to the generic 'market for silky fibres'. This dataset should not be used if it's contribution to the overall result is important.</text>
        </generalComment>
      </activity>
